翠華成日有人屌，有次去試下係咪真係咁差<br />\n<br />\n屌真係好難食，同街邊茶餐廳差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n反而去試太興，係出奇地唔差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而且同類型既食物，太興都係平5-10蚊<br />\n<br />\n雖然都唔係平，起碼唔係貴，翠華d價真係睇到呆左"},{"pid":"b22403f0092b76a2accedc98ad55ea33e38aa2ca","tid":1264954,"uid":5890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ab9f6622b7f8ab0873a115ca158a14f41a0982a7","tid":1264954,"uid":22741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"668df6c36a4ae81ffa134054bc1a5877c68f6d6d","tid":1264954,"uid":212681,"like":20,"dislike":2,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T03:56:52.000Z","msg":"改名做乜乜冰室，再裝修做懷舊風，一定大撚把人幫襯"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T05:02:02.000Z","msg":"已經做緊翠華冰室<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T05:36:00.000Z","msg":"筲箕灣個間已經係，無冷氣既屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cd99278ba5e174bda48ab19e4f73b0ea3672bd3","tid":1264954,"uid":129474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T05:42:00.000Z","msg":"由2013年未上市已經決定永不幫襯。早餐成四十幾蚊個，乜都唔轉得，侍仔串過馬撚，附近有其他茶餐廳，都只係三十蚊個早餐，粉麵餐肉腸仔全部自由配搭，點解我仲要幫襯佢?"},{"pid":"1675aac1fd14e46ccb66bbeba29e07572c15e714","tid":1264954,"uid":120913,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T05:44:37.000Z","msg":"非常好<br />\n屌你老味叫你落單辛苦到好似叫你幫我含咁<br />\n執9左佢啦"},{"pid":"95b059a209f14307d28fa872f30d31ce677bd3be","tid":1264954,"uid":187493,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T05:52:20.000Z","msg":"老實講翠華真係沒食過，中學個時覺得貴唔食。出嚟做野之後就覺得，同樣價錢我食其他野唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccafb7b41404cdddafbd9a